description: Once you have mastered the "Tempo with bursts" workout, then you are ready to up the ante a little and ride at Sweetspot and then do the bursts!   Warm-up for 10minutes and then do 3 x 1 minute fast pedaling drills >110rpm,  then do 40minutes at Sweetspot 90% of FTP, and every two minutes, do a burst for 20 seconds to 120% of FTP and resume at 90% of FTP.  Cool down.
